	"name": "Survivor (Rover)",
	"type": "feature",
	"img": "icons/magic/nature/stealth-hide-eyes-green.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You have reached a level of survival expertise and will to live that makes you qualified to teach even other rangers. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Strength, Dexterity, or Wisdom score increases by +1 to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain an expertise die with the Survival skill. Your maximum expertise die for Survival becomes a d10.</p></li><li><p>Your exertion pool increases by 1.</p></li><li><p>You can go a number of days equal to your proficiency bonus without suffering fatigue from lack of supply. This stacks with similar features such as the Forsaken culture’s Eat Like a Bird feature.</p></li></ul>",
